t started is a publisher ID from Eventbrite. Eventbrite API shutdown right now. Please refer this before purchasing addon.        </div>\n	</div>  \n    </a></div>\n    	\n    \n</div>\n\n				\n					\n<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6\">\n    <div class=\"product-listing-box\">  \n	<a href=\"https://wp-eventmanager.com/product/wp-event-manager-organizers/\" class=\"woocommerce-LoopProduct-link woocommerce-loop-product__link\">	<div class=\"product-image\">\n	<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://mk0wpeventmanag0sirn.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/plugins-icons/organizers-300x300.png\" class=\"attachment-woocommerce_thumbnail size-woocommerce_thumbnail\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n	<div class=\"product-details\">\n	    <div class=\"product-title\">\n	    <h3>\n	Organizers</h3>\n        </div>\n    \n  \n  <div class=\"product-price\">\n	\n    <span class=\"price\"><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\"><span class=\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">₹</span>1.444</span></span>  </div>\n	    <div class=\"product-short-description\">\n        Organisers add-on allows you to manage your organizer’s list and the events as per the organizer. You can show congregated and alphabetized list of all the organizers along with complete active events and list of organizers        </div>\n	</div>  \n    </a></div>\n    	\n    \n</div>\n\n				\n			</ul>', 'no'),
